These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, tomato, papaya
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Food   | tomato | papaya | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Birthday   | march | september | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, van, bike
1. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Transport   | train | van | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
